---
title: Chicken Gyros & Oregano Fries with Feta & Tzatziki
description: A beloved dish from the Mediterranean is hitting your table tonight. Wrap up a bunch of flavours in a toasty flatbread,
such as garlic and herb chicken, spinach and feta. The serving of oregano fries isn’t just a side dish tonight, try adding a few to the gyros to bring everything together.

